data.description: WELCOME TO YOUR NEW BEGINNING! You'll want to make plans to come see this charming ranch-style home conveniently located in the heart of beautiful Pensacola. This painted brick residence features 4 bedrooms, 2 full bathrooms, a large back yard, and sits just a few blocks from interstate 110...placing you only 15 minutes from the white sands of Pensacola Beach!  As a bonus, there are several "flex rooms" that would convert into the PERFECT space for an office, play room, or whatever area your lifestyle might demand. Thoughtfully updated, it's "turn-key" and ready for your family. Enjoy granite countertops in an updated kitchen, luxury vinyl plank flooring, updated bathrooms, a 2021 roof, a deck in the backyard- the list goes on! Set up your showing today before this one is gone.
